Class DataUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fusionlab.utilities.DataUtil

  • public class DataUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is mainly responsible for Data manipulation from Excel Sheet. This class Receive testcase name from DataProvide class and return data in the form of Key and Value Pair.
